window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>New enemies. Unlikely allies. A neon city in the Deadlands that never sleeps.</b></p> <p>Halek Cain has mysteries to solve, people to rescue, and a vendetta to carry out.</p> <p>But he must fix his Reaper augmentations before they kill him. He needs raw materials from Gronic, a technical specialist on Roxo III, and time to put himself right before the Union comes for him.</p> <p>Everything seems like it’s going to work out...until he learns Elise is in trouble.</p> <p>If Cain doesn’t get to her first, everything that happened on Dreadmax will have been for nothing.</p> <p>The Last Reaper will encounter assassins, Union special operators, and a mysterious rival from his past. The odds are overwhelming, and the enemies are mounting.</p> <p>But when all is said and done, each of them will learn that you must always fear the Reaper.</p>"; 
